column2: Lots of boat use and public beach use.
Lake low judging from level on shore.
Water level is down approximately 14-16" by shoreline observation.
Some people would not swim in lake now
Reading was at 2' with the lake level high with brown stained water. Perception was #2
Small flecks of algae floating in the lake starting about ten ft out. Clear at shore line on north shore.
Pieces of algae floating in the lake. Solid thick green at the inlet

Lake effervescent pea green and thick from shoreline to about 20 feet out. After that water is full small green globules. Lake effervescent pea green and thick from shoreline to about 20 feet out. After that water is full small green globules.
Lake is clear with some small algae globules floating in the water. Breezy
Beautiful day with little breeze. Quiet on lake
Outside temp is 58F. North shore is all green and algae flecks all over the lake.
Gusty winds day before removing last of ice off the lake. This day was calm sunny with air temperature of 54F.
Sunny- calm and outside temp 72 F.   One small motorboat on lake. Small bits algae suspended in water but surface is clear.

Partly cloudy- air temp 75F- one small fishing boat and one kayak on lake. Calm. Partly cloudy- air temp 75F- one small fishing boat and one kayak on lake. Calm. Small pieces of algae in water but no surface algae seen.
Air temp 81F. Very calm- partly sunny. Algae evident in water column but not on surface. 2 boaters on the lake.

Outside temp is 70. Mostly sunny with soft breeze. Green bloom along north shore.. otherwise algae seen in water column but not on the surface.  Outside temp is 70. Mostly sunny with soft breeze. Green bloom along north shore.. otherwise algae seen in water column but not on the surface. Chlorophyll and phosphorus samples collected today.
